  "title": "ACCOUNTING MANAGER (FINANCE DEPARTMENT)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Ensure compliance with relevant accounting standards, tax regulations, and internal policies.</li><li>Contribute to the development and implementation of financial controls and procedures.</li><li>Manage the preparation of financial statements, budgets, and forecasts for construction projects.</li><li>Analyse financial data, identify trends, and provide insights to support strategic decision-making.</li><li>Collaborate with project managers and other stakeholders to provide financial guidance and support.</li><li>Oversee the accounts receivable and payable processes, ensuring timely collection and payments.</li><li>Manage the financial reporting and auditing processes for construction projects.</li><li>Mentor and develop the finance team, fostering a positive and productive work environment.</li></ul><p>For interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <a href=\"mailto:davidnhbsg@gmail.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; </strong></a><strong>ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshingroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
